description: The FTSE 250 Total Return Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: British blue chip companies listed in GBP on the London Stock Exchange The 250 biggest companies outside the FTSE 100 Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.ftse.com
